# User Guardrails
- Do not create commits or run `git push` unless the user explicitly requests it.
- Before validating backend changes, run `make backend-ci`; for frontend changes, run `make frontend-ci`, unless the user indicates otherwise.
- Always mention if relevant tests remain unexecuted.
